<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="hu">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Skyhigh AI | Csomagok</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        body { background-color: #050505; color: white; font-family: sans-serif; }
        .tier-card { 
            background: #0f0f11; border: 1px solid #27272a; border-radius: 20px; padding: 30px; 
            transition: 0.3s; position: relative; overflow: hidden; display: flex; flex-direction: column;
        }
        .tier-card:hover { transform: translateY(-5px); border-color: #555; }
        .popular { border: 2px solid #a855f7; box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.15); transform: scale(1.05); z-index: 10; }
        .btn-pay { background: white; color: black; font-weight: 800; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 15px; border-radius: 10px; width: 100%; margin-top: auto; transition: 0.2s; }
        .btn-pay:hover { background: #d4d4d8; }
        .btn-purple { background: #a855f7; color: white; border: none; }
        .btn-purple:hover { background: #9333ea; }
        .price-tag { font-size: 28px; font-weight: 900; color: white; }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="p-6 max-w-7xl mx-auto flex flex-col justify-center min-h-screen">

    <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <a href="/dashboard" class="text-zinc-500 hover:text-white uppercase font-bold text-xs mb-6 block"><i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i> Vissza</a>
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-black uppercase italic mb-4">Válassz <span class="text-purple-500">Stratégiát</span></h1>
        <p class="text-zinc-400">Automatikus aktiválás azonnal a fizetés után.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 items-center">
        
        <div class="tier-card opacity-80 hover:opacity-100">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-zinc-300 mb-2">Havi</h3>
            <div class="price-tag">20.000 Ft <span class="text-xs font-normal text-zinc-500">/ hó</span></div>
            <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 mb-6">Próbáld ki kockázat nélkül.</p>
            <ul class="space-y-4 text-sm text-zinc-400 mb-8">
                <li><i class="fas fa-check text-zinc-500 mr-2"></i> 30 napos licenc</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-check text-zinc-500 mr-2"></i> Napi Master Tipp</li>
            </ul>
            <form action="/pay/create-checkout-session" method="POST">
                <input type="hidden" name="plan" value="monthly">
                <button type="submit" class="btn-pay">Kiválasztás</button>
            </form>
        </div>

        <div class="tier-card popular bg-[#121214]">
            <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 bg-purple-600 text-white text-[10px] font-bold px-4 py-1 rounded-bl-xl uppercase">Ajánlott</div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-purple-400 mb-1 uppercase">Profi Stratégia</h3>
            <div class="price-tag">100.000 Ft <span class="text-xs font-normal text-zinc-400">/ 6 hó</span></div>
            <p class="text-xs text-green-500 font-bold mb-6">Spórolj 20.000 Ft-ot!</p>
            <ul class="space-y-4 text-sm text-white mb-8">
                <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-purple-500 mr-2"></i> <strong>180 napos</strong> profit</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-purple-500 mr-2"></i> <strong>Stratégiai Mentorálás</strong></li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-purple-500 mr-2"></i> Kiemelt Support</li>
            </ul>
            <form action="/pay/create-checkout-session" method="POST">
                <input type="hidden" name="plan" value="biannual">
                <button type="submit" class="btn-pay btn-purple shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(168,85,247,0.4)]">Profi Leszek</button>
            </form>
        </div>

        <div class="tier-card opacity-80 hover:opacity-100">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-zinc-300 mb-2">Befektető</h3>
            <div class="price-tag">180.000 Ft <span class="text-xs font-normal text-zinc-500">/ év</span></div>
            <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 mb-6">A legnagyobb megtakarítás.</p>
            <ul class="space-y-4 text-sm text-zinc-400 mb-8">
                <li><i class="fas fa-check text-zinc-500 mr-2"></i> 365 napos licenc</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-check text-zinc-500 mr-2"></i> VIP bánásmód</li>
            </ul>
            <form action="/pay/create-checkout-session" method="POST">
                <input type="hidden" name="plan" value="annual">
                <button type="submit" class="btn-pay">Kiválasztás</button>
            </form>
        </div>

    </div>
</body>
</html>